{"tid":2451560,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"［善用不推文回覆］2021 DSE雞+non jupaa 樹仁大學入學不完全攻略","createTime":"2021-03-18T07:55:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T11:14:09.000Z","uid":236080,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cc04213477741692382870e4a8f7e408ba876908","tid":2451560,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:55:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">樹大招瘋</span></span></strong><br />\n首先唔好聽人講話：樹仁師資好 又有人情味 Can啲嘢唔差 Hall又望海幾正<br />\n<br />\n假㗎屌你 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入得嚟嘅DSE雞/HD/ASSO仔都係2個原因：<br />\n<br />\n1）你覺得自己廢，入唔到UGC<br />\n<br />\n2）你當樹仁係水泡<br />\n<br />\n無論1定2都好，聽一聽以下內容先決定係咪揀樹。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">入學要求：</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nDSE入學：除咗社工同新傳，其他33222就得<br />\nNon jupad入學：社工新傳應該3.0-3.4 左右 / 其他科就2.5以上都得，聽過某文科收過below 2.5<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">學費：</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n數一數二貴，但平過含大<br />\n<br />\n近年政府出咗nmtss，會資助你3萬幾蚊學費，唔洗還<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Nmtss 申請條件：</strong><br />\n<br />\n1）DSE畢業：有33222就得<br />\n2）non jupas：要ASSO /HD畢業先有<br />\n<br />\n滿足以上其中一個條件就得，攞完依可以申請其他政府資助。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>U life:</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1）玩校隊：唔熟，但足球隊好似幾抽得（非打手）<br />\n2）上莊：咪撚上莊，上莊正戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n#見人見志，你自己去r嘢玩就一定有u life。但奉勸大家唔好上大莊，好撚閪，u life大把選擇，但千祈唔好上大莊，浪費時間金錢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>Canteen：</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1）Donka：貴 / 唔算屎 / 貴價版大家樂大快活咁<br />\n2）Pacific coffee：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不了<br />\n<br />\n#其實foodpanda銅鑼灣北角大把嘢飲大把嘢食，行落條斜路去賽西湖有平靚正飯食，囍筷&hellip;.仲有其他<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>翻學放學交通：</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1）小巴（25銅鑼灣/49m天后站）：去到賽西湖公園執牌叫巴士站落就得，唔好戇鳩鳩跟人係賽西湖大廈落，行多啲啲路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2）巴士（108過海紅磡/27落北角/25中環五號碼頭/25a去灣仔北&hellip;&hellip;不能盡錄）<br />\n<br />\n3）的士<br />\n<br />\n4）校巴（冇坐過，校網有時間表，$4.5 一程）<br />\n<br />\n#係donka出面有部巴士八達窿機，拍一拍下程又慳翻啲錢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>GPA：</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1）速度唔洗諗，咁多間u最慢一定係樹仁<br />\n<br />\n2）killer見過2個，點做點交齊考埋試都係C<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>有咩科好讀：</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1）入樹就SW 同 新傳啦，前者有牌後者樹仁好多資源<br />\n2）你有興趣咪讀純心/輔心，但出路一定冇上兩者好<br />\n3）中英文社會學歷史系，唔清楚，但上過啲選修覺得幾fun<br />\n4）<span class=\"red\">記住樹仁讀完LAW B畢業唔係律師嚟</span><br />\n5）點解要係樹仁讀BBA&hellip;&hellip;.<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />資源又少 出路又輸俾8大同含大<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>交學費：</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n樹仁冇得網上用信用卡俾錢<br />\n<br />\n1）親身交支票<br />\n2）親身交支票<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>HALL係點：</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1）Hall好唔好住？<br />\n舊Hall冇碌架床，爽啲但污糟啲<br />\n新Hall有碌架床，睇你鍾唔鍾意扮上扮落，但乾淨係真<br />\n<br />\n2）Hall有冇NDS（內地生）<br />\n緊係有，不過樹依家好似NDS同local分層，自從多年前成班local圍鳩個nds<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3）樹仁HALL有咩最on9?<br />\n樹仁平均每10個宿生就有3個唔識用微波爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4）真係望到海？你估個個都最高層啊，低層望閪到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">咁多位！DSE加油！無論點都好，未到絕望一刻都唔好揀樹仁<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"95eb9e52f98d89da1bde05357890c40ecec900a0","tid":2451560,"uid":236080,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:57:05.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">仲有個校徽好撚柒</span><br />\n<br />\n間學校又細<br />\n<br />\n成間中學咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n來生不做樹仁人"},{"pid":"6da0fa3217c6b781d65da98a7909860d65bc2ec2","tid":2451560,"uid":236080,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:58:06.000Z","msg":"樹仁係咪好多女？女多過男？啲女正唔正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你老母仲靚，女多過男只係過去，依家都已經5050"},{"pid":"1d82d9dc695778add2b7dfead74d4126b01117d0","tid":2451560,"uid":210944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T10:55:23.000Z","msg":"總之唔好入<br />\n我淨係in過都覺得唔掂"},{"pid":"e928cb9269cd3ff05e40ae249742231b6ee4d7c0","tid":2451560,"uid":322578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T17:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ed3b46b0d73ebb54d9efc4747f39d5d834c546c","tid":2451560,"uid":236080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e928cb9269cd3ff05e40ae249742231b6ee4d7c0","tid":2451560,"uid":322578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T17:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T17:45:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0b271427d6b36a04d342b81bf6d6c18827de1c","tid":2451560,"uid":322578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ed3b46b0d73ebb54d9efc4747f39d5d834c546c","tid":2451560,"uid":236080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e928cb9269cd3ff05e40ae249742231b6ee4d7c0","tid":2451560,"uid":322578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T17:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T17:45:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"